data.name: Tomato Basil Bruschetta
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and flavorful appetizer featuring crunchy toasted bread topped with a tangy tomato and basil mixture.
detailedCookingInstructions: Slice the baguette into 1/2 inch thick slices and place on a baking sheet.
Brush both sides of the bread slices with olive oil.
Toast in the oven for about 5 minutes or until golden and crispy.
In a bowl, combine diced tomatoes, chopped basil, minced garlic, balsamic vinegar, salt, and pepper.
Spoon the tomato mixture generously onto each toasted bread slice and serve immediately.
data.modifiersForBase: Topped with Tomato and Basil mixture
